C

Component - Class in pa.iscde.configurator.model
This class represents a component(bundle) that is running, has a view and is related to the project to represent on ConfiguratorView It is created by the class Constructor.java in the package pa.iscde.configurator.controller
Component(String, boolean) - Constructor for class pa.iscde.configurator.model.Component
Class constructor Creates a component specifying id name and a boolean that indicates if he's running or not this boolean exists to be possible, in the future, to create components that aren't running and differentiate them from those who are running
ConfiguratorView - Class in pa.iscde.configurator.view
This class is used to represent the view of the bundle pa.iscde.configurator When ConfiguratorView starts, it creates the controller to get information from him about running components and dependencies between them.
ConfiguratorView() - Constructor for class pa.iscde.configurator.view.ConfiguratorView
 
Constructor - Class in pa.iscde.configurator.controller
This class creates the model classes that represent the components and dependencies to paint This class is created by the controller and uses a class Platform to get the information (components, dependencies and their attributes) from.
Constructor() - Constructor for class pa.iscde.configurator.controller.Constructor
 
Controller - Class in pa.iscde.configurator.controller
This class is used as an intermediary between the view and the data classes Represents the Controller on MVC architecture It is created when the view is opened and gives the view the classes of data to represent.
Controller() - Constructor for class pa.iscde.configurator.controller.Controller
Constructor of the class Controller when created, it starts the Constructor and get the data from him.
createComponents() - Method in class pa.iscde.configurator.controller.Constructor
This method creates all the components related to pt.iscte.pidesco that have a view and are running
createContents(Composite, Map<String, Image>) - Method in class pa.iscde.configurator.view.ConfiguratorView
 
createDependencies(LinkedList<Component>) - Method in class pa.iscde.configurator.controller.Constructor
This method creates all the dependencies related to the components passed by parameter Only creates dependencies if the main component or the dependent exist on the list.
